web_snippets: Estella Atekwana (née Estella Akweseh Nkwate; born 13 September 1961) is a geophysicist studying biogeophysics and tectonophysics.
Founder and co-owner of Estella, a luxury kids clothing company based in New York City - www.estella-nyc.com.
Estella is a Christian with The Apostolic Church (TAC) where she is a preacher and counsellor/intercessor. She enjoys playing tennis and listening to gospel ...
